:: 3) directory organization ::

(directory names represented in ALL CAPS here)

index.php				- the solitary executed script of the application
CORE					- contains application code, not harmoni specific
HARMONI					- contains the mechanics of the harmoni code
	Config.class.php	- class that handles accessing app config props
	Context.class.php	- class that handles where a user is in the application
	Form.class.php		- class that handles form processing and validation
	Harmoni.class.php	- controller object that provides harmoni services
	Layout.class.php	- class that handles laying out html print content
	User.class.php		- class that handles user information
	SERVICES			- contains services provided by harmoni but not
						  manditory to use
	UTILITIES			- contains classes used by harmoni and available to
						  application programmers
LAYOUTS					- contains the layout templates
MODULES					- contains the application modules